          <head type="note" n="1" xml:id="spp-438-321L-headnote-1">
            <lg n="1" xml:id="spp-438-321L-headnote-1-line-group-1" type="headnote">
              <l n="1" xml:id="spp-438-321L-headnote-1-line-group-1-line-1">To the Tune of Sally in our Ally.&#13;</l>
            </lg>
          </head>
          <head type="note" n="2" xml:id="spp-438-321L-headnote-2">
            <lg n="1" xml:id="spp-438-321L-headnote-2-line-group-1" type="headnote">
              <l n="1" xml:id="spp-438-321L-headnote-2-line-group-1-line-1">1728.</l>
            </lg>
          </head>
          <head type="note" n="3" xml:id="spp-438-321L-headnote-3">
            <lg n="1" xml:id="spp-438-321L-headnote-3-line-group-1" type="headnote">
              <l n="1" xml:id="spp-438-321L-headnote-3-line-group-1-line-1"></l>
            </lg>
          </head>
          <lg n="1">
            <l rend="center indent(1)" xml:id="swift-438-321L-line-1" n="1">1.<lb/>All you that wou'd</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-438-321L-line-2" n="2">Refine your Blood,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-438-321L-line-3" n="3">As pure as fam'd Luellin,</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-438-321L-line-4" n="4">By Waters clear;</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-438-321L-line-5" n="5">Come once a Year</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-438-321L-line-6" n="6">To drink at Ballyspellin.</l>
            <l rend="center indent(1)" xml:id="swift-438-321L-line-7" n="7">2.<lb/>If Pox or Itch</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-438-321L-line-8" n="8">Your Skins inrich</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-438-321L-line-9" n="9">With Rubies past the telling;</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-438-321L-line-10" n="10">'Twill cure your Skin,</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-438-321L-line-11" n="11">Before you've been,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-438-321L-line-12" n="12">A Month at Ballyspellin.</l>
            <l rend="center indent(1)" xml:id="swift-438-321L-line-13" n="13">3.<lb/>If Lady's Cheek</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-438-321L-line-14" n="14">Be green as Leek</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-438-321L-line-15" n="15">When she comes from her Dwelling,</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-438-321L-line-16" n="16">The kindling Rose</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-438-321L-line-17" n="17">Within it blows</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-438-321L-line-18" n="18">When she's at Ballyspelling.</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-438-321L-line-19" n="19">«FL»4.<lb/>«FL»The sooty Brown</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-438-321L-line-20" n="20">That comes from Town</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-438-321L-line-21" n="21">Grows here as fair as Hellen;</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-438-321L-line-22" n="22">Then back she goes</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-438-321L-line-23" n="23">To kill the Beaux,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-438-321L-line-24" n="24">By Dint of Ballyspelling.</l>
            <l rend="center indent(1)" xml:id="swift-438-321L-line-25" n="25">5.<lb/>All Ladies here</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-438-321L-line-26" n="26">Are fresh and fair</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-438-321L-line-27" n="27">As Ross, or bright Dunkellin;</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-438-321L-line-28" n="28">And Mars might make</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-438-321L-line-29" n="29">A fair Mistake,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-438-321L-line-30" n="30">Were he at Ballyspellin.</l>
            <l rend="center indent(1)" xml:id="swift-438-321L-line-31" n="31">6.We Men submit</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-438-321L-line-32" n="32">As they think fit,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-438-321L-line-33" n="33">And here is no rebelling;</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-438-321L-line-34" n="34">The Reason's plain,</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-438-321L-line-35" n="35">The Lady's reign,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-438-321L-line-36" n="36">They're Queens at Ballyspellin.</l>
            <l rend="center indent(1)" xml:id="swift-438-321L-line-37" n="37">7.By matchless Charms</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-438-321L-line-38" n="38">Unconquer'd Arms</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-438-321L-line-39" n="39">They have the Power of quelling</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-438-321L-line-40" n="40">Such desperate Foes</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-438-321L-line-41" n="41">As dare oppose</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-438-321L-line-42" n="42">Their Power at Ballyspellin.</l>
            <l rend="center indent(1)" xml:id="swift-438-321L-line-43" n="43">8.Cold Water turns</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-438-321L-line-44" n="44">To Fire, and burns,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-438-321L-line-45" n="45">I know, because I fell in</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-438-321L-line-46" n="46">A Stream which came</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-438-321L-line-47" n="47">From one bright Dame,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-438-321L-line-48" n="48">Who drank at Ballyspellin.</l>
            <l rend="center indent(1)" xml:id="swift-438-321L-line-49" n="49">9.Fine Beaux advance</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-438-321L-line-50" n="50">Equipt for Dance,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-438-321L-line-51" n="51">And bring their Ann or Nell in,</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-438-321L-line-52" n="52">With so much Grace,</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-438-321L-line-53" n="53">I'm sure no place</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-438-321L-line-54" n="54">Can vie with Ballyspellin.</l>
            <l rend="center indent(1)" xml:id="swift-438-321L-line-55" n="55">10.No Politicks,</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-438-321L-line-56" n="56">No subtle Tricks,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-438-321L-line-57" n="57">No Man his Country selling,</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-438-321L-line-58" n="58">We eat, we drink,</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-438-321L-line-59" n="59">We never think</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-438-321L-line-60" n="60">Of these at Ballyspellin.</l>
            <l rend="center indent(1)" xml:id="swift-438-321L-line-61" n="61">11.The troubl'd in Mind</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-438-321L-line-62" n="62">The puff'd with Wind,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-438-321L-line-63" n="63">Do all come here Pell-mell in,</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-438-321L-line-64" n="64">And they are sure</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-438-321L-line-65" n="65">To work their Cure,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-438-321L-line-66" n="66">By drinking Ballyspellin.</l>
            <l rend="center indent(1)" xml:id="swift-438-321L-line-67" n="67">12.If Dropsy fills</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-438-321L-line-68" n="68">You to the Gills,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-438-321L-line-69" n="69">From Top to Toe tho' swelling,</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-438-321L-line-70" n="70">Pour in, pour out,</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-438-321L-line-71" n="71">You'll find, no doubt,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-438-321L-line-72" n="72">A Cure at Ballyspellin.</l>
            <l rend="center indent(1)" xml:id="swift-438-321L-line-73" n="73">13.Thro' all these Parts</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-438-321L-line-74" n="74">Death throws no Darts,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-438-321L-line-75" n="75">No Sexton's here a Knelling;</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-438-321L-line-76" n="76">Come judge and try</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-438-321L-line-77" n="77">You'll never die,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-438-321L-line-78" n="78">But live at Ballyspellin.</l>
            <l rend="center indent(1)" xml:id="swift-438-321L-line-79" n="79">14.Except you feel</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-438-321L-line-80" n="80">Darts tipt with Steel,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-438-321L-line-81" n="81">Which here are ev'ry Belle in,</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-438-321L-line-82" n="82">When from their Eyes</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-438-321L-line-83" n="83">Sweet Ruin flies,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-438-321L-line-84" n="84">We die at Ballyspellin.</l>
            <l rend="center indent(1)" xml:id="swift-438-321L-line-85" n="85">15.Good Cheer, sweet Air,</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-438-321L-line-86" n="86">Much Ioy, no Care,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-438-321L-line-87" n="87">Your Taste, your Sight, your Smelling,</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-438-321L-line-88" n="88">Your Ears, your Touch,</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-438-321L-line-89" n="89">Transported much</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-438-321L-line-90" n="90">Each day at Ballyspelling.</l>
            <l rend="center indent(1)" xml:id="swift-438-321L-line-91" n="91">16.Within this Ground,</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-438-321L-line-92" n="92">All Folks sleep sound,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-438-321L-line-93" n="93">No noisy Dogs a yelling,</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-438-321L-line-94" n="94">Except you wake,</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-438-321L-line-95" n="95">For Cælia's Sake,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-438-321L-line-96" n="96">All night at Ballyspellin.</l>
            <l rend="center indent(1)" xml:id="swift-438-321L-line-97" n="97">17.Here All you see,</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-438-321L-line-98" n="98">Both he and she,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-438-321L-line-99" n="99">No Lady keeps her Cell in,</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-438-321L-line-100" n="100">But all partake</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-438-321L-line-101" n="101">The Mirth we make</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-438-321L-line-102" n="102">Who drink at Ballyspellin.</l>
            <l rend="center indent(1)" xml:id="swift-438-321L-line-103" n="103">18.My Rhimes are gone,</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-438-321L-line-104" n="104">I think I'·ve none,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-438-321L-line-105" n="105">Except I should bring Hell in;</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-438-321L-line-106" n="106">But since I'm here,</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-438-321L-line-107" n="107">To Heav'n so near,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-438-321L-line-108" n="108">I can't at Ballyspellin.</l>
          </lg>
        </div>
      </div>
